David Kirkpatrick , author of "The 
Facebook Effect," says Facebook remains "opaque" as a public 
company. Kirkpatrick talks with Bloomberg's Tom Keene, Sara 
Eisen and Scarlet Fu on Bloomberg Radio's "Bloomberg 
Surveillance."     (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 06:06
 